#
# === DIVERGENCES vs rmxOS (for op-116-cont semantics-diff) ===
#  #1 asl_close return type: macOS void (Apple asl.h, deprecated->os_log) vs rmxOS int.
#     Compile-level; the harness's `asl_close(c) == 0` is portable only if asl_close returns int.
#     Candidate fix: harness use `asl_close(c); R("asl_close", 1);` (op-116's call) OR rmxOS align
